Hokuriku Electric Industry is issuing a35 mln dlr equity warrant bond due May 7, 1992 paying anindicated coupon of 2-1/8 pct and priced at par, lead managerNomura International Ltd said.    The issue is guaranteed by Hokuriku Bank Ltd. The sellingconcession is 1-1/2 pct while management and underwritingcombined pays 3/4 pct. Final terms are due April 16.    The payment date is May 7 and the issue is available indenominations of 5,000 dlrs. Listing will be in Luxembourg. REUTER&#3;